- cs.Distributed is another possible category as the paper focuses on distributed resource utilization. 
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is a possible category as the paper discusses the need for a well-defined conceptual model of Pilot-Jobs. 
- cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science) is a possible category as the paper applies the P* Model to Pilot-Data.
